           <div class="drycappuccino-heading">
               <h1> Black Coffee</h1>
               <p>A dry cappuccino has the basic layers of the standard cup but with different proportions. Instead of having equal parts espresso, steamed milk, and foamed milk, a dry cappuccino has very little steamed milk and a lot more foam. This is why it’s called dry as the foam is the least dense (liquid) portion of the drink.</p>
